104
00:13:18.416 --> 00:13:19.584
A bullet.

105
00:13:29.327 --> 00:13:30.361
Relax.

106
00:13:32.998 --> 00:13:34.599
Nobody has a mask here.

107
00:13:50.448 --> 00:13:51.984
(EXHALES)

108
00:13:59.290 --> 00:14:00.625
